examples.q: Top 25 subjects by number of ED visits (show subject_id and count).
examples.sql:
SELECT
  ed.subject_id,
  COUNT(*) AS num_ed_visits
FROM physionet-data.mimiciv_ed.edstays AS ed
GROUP BY ed.subject_id
ORDER BY num_ed_visits DESC
LIMIT 25

examples.q: Top 10 primary ED diagnoses by title.
examples.sql:
SELECT
  d.icd_title AS cause,
  COUNT(*) AS n
FROM physionet-data.mimiciv_ed.diagnosis AS d
WHERE d.seq_num = 1 AND d.icd_title IS NOT NULL
GROUP BY cause
ORDER BY n DESC
LIMIT 10

examples.q: Monthly ED visit counts across the full range, ordered by month.
examples.sql:
SELECT
  DATE_TRUNC(ed.intime, MONTH) AS month,
  COUNT(*) AS n
FROM physionet-data.mimiciv_ed.edstays AS ed
GROUP BY month
ORDER BY month

SELECT
  ed.esi,
  COUNTIF(ed.hadm_id IS NOT NULL) / COUNT(*) AS admit_rate,
  COUNT(*) AS n
FROM physionet-data.mimiciv_ed.edstays AS ed
WHERE ed.esi IS NOT NULL
GROUP BY ed.esi
ORDER BY ed.esi
